Interface BeanTableModel<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the class representing a row in the table
    All Superinterfaces:
    TableModel
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ChangeBufferTableModel<T>, SectionTableModel<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface BeanTableModel<T>
extends TableModel
    Interface for a TableModel that uses a list of beans for the row data.
